## The 7 pillars (non-negotiable)

1. **Plan before code** — run `/eo-plan` before writing any feature
2. **Subagents for parallel work** — dispatch when files are independent
3. **Lessons compound** — append to `.claude/lessons.md` after every correction
4. **Verify before done** — `/eo-review` before declaring complete
5. **Demand elegance** — elegance-pause block in every non-trivial PR
6. **Autonomous bug fixing** — `/eo-debug` finds root cause + regression test
7. **Score + ship** — 90+ composite or don't ship

## Daily command chain

| Step | Command | Gate |
|------|---------|------|
| Plan | `/eo-plan {feature}` | Approval |
| Code | `/eo-code` | Tests pass |
| Review | `/eo-review` | No 🔴 items |
| Score | `/eo-score` | 90+ composite |
| Fix gaps | `/eo-bridge-gaps` | Lowest hat ≥8 |
| Ship | `/eo-ship` | Health check 200 |
| Retro | `/eo-retro` | Weekly |
| Debug | `/eo-debug {bug}` | On-demand |

## Quality gate
- No PR without 90+ composite score (saved to `docs/qa-scores/`)
- No hat below 8
- Elegance pause block in commit description
- BRD traceability 100% for "done" ACs

## MENA rules (applies if ICP is MENA)
- Arabic-first UI, `dir="rtl"` respected
- Fonts: Cairo (headers), Tajawal (body)
- Mobile 375px tested before ≥8 UX hat
- Dates DD/MM/YYYY, weekend Fri/Sat
- Currency: AED/SAR/QAR (KWD uses 3 decimals)
- No alcohol/pork/revealing imagery
- Ramadan-aware scheduling

## Words forbidden in UI
leverage, synergy, ecosystem, holistic, digital transformation, innovative, cutting-edge, world-class, best-in-class

## Voice
Direct. Specific. Numbers over claims. Trust-first, pitch-second.

## Env vars
See `.env.example`. Never commit `.env.local`.

## Deploy
- Server: {SERVER}
- Path: {SERVER_PATH}
- PM2 process: {PM2_NAME}
- Command: `git pull && npm ci && npm run build && pm2 reload {PM2_NAME}`
- Never edit directly on server. Always local → GitHub → server pull.

## Git discipline
- Branches: `main` (prod), `dev` (integration), `feat/*` (features)
- Conventional commits: feat/fix/docs/chore
- Every PR: elegance pause block, BRD ACs referenced, score report attached
- Never commit: `.env.local`, `node_modules/`, `.next/`, secrets

## Session bootstrap
Lessons at `.claude/lessons.md` auto-load via SessionStart hook. Read them before every plan.

## When stuck
1. Check `.claude/lessons.md` — have I hit this before?
2. Check `docs/qa-scores/trend.csv` — which hat keeps failing?
3. Run `/eo-debug` with specific error
4. Ask in EO MicroSaaS community Slack

## Non-negotiable
- No code without a BRD
- No ship without 90+ score
- No bug fix without regression test
- No new dep without bundle-size comment
- No UI PR without mobile + Arabic screenshots (if MENA)
